data.description: Large Brick home with approx 1836 sq ft that's situated at the end of a hidden private shared road, with County Tax only! This spacious home comes with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, living room, den, kitchen/dining combo and a large fenced backyard with 2 storage sheds. The HVAC is less than 3 yrs old. The location is prime near Hacks Cross & Shelby Dr., just minutes from FedEx World HQ, Shopping and Schools. Home can go FHA, VA and Conventional, so bring your best offer.
